1. What Is Luma?

Luma is an event management and community platform that lets individuals and organizations create beautiful event pages, handle RSVPs, sell tickets, and run virtual or in-person gatherings — all with a single shareable link.
luma.com

Instead of clunky forms or disconnected tools, Luma provides polished landing pages where guests can view details and register. It’s become popular with meetups, tech communities, and networking events for its simplicity and design-first focus.
